# Expense Operating Amortisation Intangible Assets Finite Life Amount

## identifier
de7504

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, during the relevant period, of amortisation charged to profit and loss in respect of intangible assets with a finite life as determined in accordance with accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Expense.Operating.AmortisationIntangibleAssetsFiniteLife.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.06
- period=duration
